OL,3,CMan charged over shopping centre bomb
OL,4,Choax
OL,6,FA man has been charged with staging a
OL,7,Fbomb hoax at a busy shopping centre.
OL,9,FPolice were called to St George's
OL,10,FShopping Centre in Preston on Monday 4
OL,11,FMay to reports of a bomb threat.
OL,13,FThe centre was searched and nothing
OL,14,Fsuspicious was found.
OL,16,FIn a separate incident, officers were
OL,17,Falso called to reports that threats
OL,18,Fhad been made to a Royal Preston
OL,19,FHospital Ward on Tuesday 5 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
