OL,3,CMan charged over shopping centre bomb
OL,4,Choax
OL,6,FEthan Hardy, 20, has been charged with
OL,7,Fsending a bomb hoax ` communicating
OL,8,Ffalse information ` in relation to St
OL,9,FGeorge's Shopping Centre, and sending
OL,10,Fcommunication threatening death or
OL,11,Fserious harm at the Royal Preston
OL,12,FHospital.
